'''史密斯威森護衞者'''（{{Lang-en|'''Smith & Wesson Bodyguard'''}}）是一系列由[[美国|美国]]槍械公司[[史密斯&威森|史密斯&威森]]所研製及生產的“J型[[机匣|底把]]”[[扳机#双动式|雙動操作]]式[[左輪手槍|左輪手槍]]，直到目前仍然生產，視乎型號而發射[[.38_Special|.38 S&W特種型]]或火力相對較強的[[.357麥格農|.357 S&W馬格南]]這二種.357[[口徑|口徑]]的[[手枪|手枪]][[子彈|子彈]]。<ref name="Boorman2002">{{cite book|last=Boorman|first=Dean K.|title=The History of Smith & Wesson Firearms|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5jnqqkW85u8C&pg=PA78|date=1 December 2002|publisher=Globe Pequot|isbn=978-1-58574-721-4|page=78}}</ref>

== 型號 ==
=== 史密斯威森M38 ===
史密斯威森M38為[[铝|铝]]製[[机匣|底把]]，並具有[[碳鋼|碳鋼]]製造的5發容量[[弹巢|弹巢]]和[[槍管|槍管]]。發射[[.38_Special|.38 S&W特種彈]]。<ref name="Ahern2010">{{cite book|last=Ahern|first=Jerry|title=Armed for Personal Defense|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=U3coK8za7q4C&pg=PA47|year=2010|publisher=Krause Publications|location=Iola, Wisconsin|isbn=1-4402-1643-6|page=47}}</ref>

=== 史密斯威森M49 ===
史密斯威森M49為全碳鋼製底把左輪手槍，發射.38 S&W特種彈。<ref name="Ahern2010"/>

=== 史密斯威森M638 ===
史密斯威森M38為铝製底把，並具有[[不鏽鋼|不鏽鋼]]製造的彈巢和槍管。發射.38 S&W特種彈。<ref name="Ahern2010"/>

=== 史密斯威森M649 ===
史密斯威森M469為全碳鋼製底把左輪手槍，發射.38 S&W特種彈或火力相對較強的[[.357麥格農|.357 S&W馬格南子彈]]。<ref name="Ahern2010"/>

=== 史密斯威森軍警型護衞者38 ===
史密斯威森軍警型護衞者38在2014年推出，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gunsandammo.com/first-look/first-look-smith-wesson-mp-bodyguard-handguns-crimson-trace-lasers/|title=First Look: Smith & Wesson M&P Bodyguard Handguns with Crimson Trace Lasers - Guns & Ammo|date=2014-07-15|website=Guns & Ammo|language=en-US|access-date=2016-05-21|archive-date=2017-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904152521/http://www.gunsandammo.com/first-look/first-look-smith-wesson-mp-bodyguard-handguns-crimson-trace-lasers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>為使用護衞者這一綽號的史密斯威森左輪手槍的最新型號。它是發射.38 S&W特種彈的[[聚合物|聚合物]]底把左輪手槍，亦是唯一可配備一體化型{{Link-en|緋紅軌跡|Crimson Trace}}[[雷射瞄準器|雷射瞄準]]握把的型號。與以前的護衞者型號一樣，它具有五發彈巢和隱藏式擊錘；但亦與以前的型號不同的是，擊錘不能待擊以作單動射擊。<ref name="Shideler2010">{{cite book|last=Shideler|first=Dan|title=Guns Illustrated 2011: The Latest Guns, Specs & Prices|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=eT2t8PBVmVMC&pg=PA58|date=20 August 2010|publisher=F+W Media, Inc|location=Iola|isbn=1-4402-1624-X|page=58}}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |url=http://ir.smith-wesson.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=90977&p=irol-newsArticle&ID=1376451&highlight= |title=Smith & Wesson(R) Introduces New BODYGUARD(R) Line. Company Launches New Compact Pistol and Revolver with Integrated Laser System |publisher=Smith & Wesson |date=2010-01-19 |accessdate=2014-08-26 }}{{Dead link|date=2020年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>其閉鎖機構亦與其他任何一款史密斯威森左輪手槍不同，而且該型號與其「J型底把」系列並無可互換使用的部件。<ref name="americanrifleman1">{{cite web |author=Wiley Clapp |url=http://www.americanrifleman.org/articles/smith-and-wesson-bodyguard-reviews |title=S&W’s New Bodyguards |publisher={{Link-en|美國槍手|American Rifleman}} |date= |accessdate=2014-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826205431/http://www.americanrifleman.org/articles/smith-and-wesson-bodyguard-reviews |archive-date=2014-08-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>發射.38 S&W特種彈。它是唯一可配備一體化型{{Link-en|緋紅軌跡|Crimson Trace}}（以前是[[透視科技公司|透視科技公司]]的）紅點[[雷射瞄準器|雷射瞄準]]握把的型號。<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.smith-wesson.com/wcsstore/SmWesson2/upload/other/MPCTFinal.pdf |title=Smith & Wesson® Introduces New M&P® BODYGUARD® Handguns with Crimson Trace® Laser Sights |publisher=Smith & Wesson Corp. |date=July 15, 2014 |accessdate=2014-08-26 |archive-date=2016-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629145423/https://www.smith-wesson.com/wcsstore/SmWesson2/upload/other/MPCTFinal.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>這槍與[[史密斯威森百週年紀念左輪手槍|S&W Centennial]]的型號最為密切相關。<ref name="americanrifleman1"/>

== 歷史和用途 ==
[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]第一任局長[[約翰·埃德加·胡佛|約翰·埃德加·胡佛]]的特別助理[[克萊德·托爾森|克萊德·托爾森]]（副局長）持有一把序列號512236的M38 Airweight，並在其中一邊刻上了他的名字。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=D8qXdU45SCUC|title=Standard Catalog of Smith & Wesson|last=Supica|first=Jim|last2=Nahas|first2=Richard|date=2007-01-03|publisher=F+W Media, Inc|isbn=089689293X|language=en}}</ref>

1968年2月1日[[越南战争|越戰]]的[[春節攻勢|春節攻勢]]期間，前[[越南共和国|越南共和国]][[越南共和國國家警察|國家警察]]總監[[阮玉鸞|阮玉鸞]]在[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]]及[[美联社|美联社]]的鏡頭前當眾在西貢街上以M38護衞者[[枪毙|枪毙]][[越共|越共]][[游击战|游擊隊]][[領袖|領袖]]{{Link-vi|阮文歛|Nguyễn Văn Lém}}。<ref name="Berryhill">{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=cDstIbV8WdsC | title=The Trials of Eroy Brown: The Murder Case That Shook the Texas Prison System | publisher=University of Texas Press | author=Berryhill, Michael | year=2011 | pages=34 | isbn=9780292742185}}</ref>捕捉到阮玉鸞扣動扳掣一刻的[[攝影師|攝影師]][[艾迪·亚当斯|艾迪·亚当斯]]，憑著這張照片奪得1969年度的[[普利策奖|普利策奖]]；而這張照片亦令公眾對越戰的看法轉變為反感。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nationalreview.com/articles/204511/there-are-tears-my-eyes/jonah-goldberg | title='There Are Tears in My Eyes', Eddie Adams & the Most Famous Photo of the Vietnam War | publisher=National Review Online | accessdate=13 November 2014 | author=Goldberg, Jonah | archive-date=2015-02-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150212065049/http://www.nationalreview.com/articles/204511/there-are-tears-my-eyes/jonah-goldberg | dead-url=no }}</ref>

1984年12月22日{{Link-en|1984年紐約地鐵槍擊案|1984 New York City Subway shooting|紐約地鐵槍擊案}}，凶手伯恩哈德·戈茨使用M38 Airweight在[[紐約地鐵|紐約地鐵]]列車內對他相信企圖向他行劫的四名年輕的黑人男子開槍。<ref>http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,141513,00.html {{Wayback|url=http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,141513,00.html |date=20200807182234 }} Time Magazine: A Troubled and Troubling Life</ref><ref>{{YouTube|d4uQJ6_00so}}</ref>

